Small ViewFullTables from Luquillo.

Source: R/data.R
vft_1quad.Rd

ViewFullTable data from Luquillo including 1 and 4 quadrats from a single census. Adapted from fgeo.data::luquillo_vft_4quad.

vft_4quad

vft_1quad

Format

An object of class tbl_df (inherits from tbl, data.frame) with 1675 rows and 32 columns.
